{"tid":102463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"366萬林寶撞七人車撼壆!車主為年輕金融才俊","createTime":"2017-01-31T15:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T17:44:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9dfe9ef7f62aaba99060bff0b67e663337f2ca4","tid":102463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"林寶跑車與七人車旺角相撞，4人受傷送院。晚上9時許，一輛林寶堅尼跑車沿旺角道西行，至香港仔魚蛋粉對開時，與一輛右轉入通菜街的七人車相撞，繼而失控撞向路中石壆，車頭凹陷損毀，車廂安全氣袋彈出，七人車則右後轆受損，意外中跑車司機、七人車3名乘客受傷，有人報警求助。救護員接報趕至，將傷者送院治理，警方正調查意外原因。 <br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料顯示，涉事林寶堅尼GALLARDO COUPE超級跑車於2009年出廠，當時車價約366萬港元，現時登記車主為一名姓李男子，登記地址為天水圍天逸邨。涉事本田Freed Aero七人車在前年落地，當時車價約23萬港元，車主登記地址為旺角嘉麗園。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/photo/bkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170129233622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170129233622&h=742284a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/bkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170129%2Fbkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001.html%20&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7LxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=12f73f88\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/bkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001.html </a>"},{"pid":"428bb1433bd76051da82192c67ee424e53da0f23","tid":102463,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得&quot;金融才俊&quot;呢四隻字係取笑緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e7e44e7ebc9527d95aac40b4b95bb280fed91d","tid":102463,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"幾年車既細牛應該同買部R35差唔多價"},{"pid":"23e7b251e992c65504d0a3fac4c6408b8d7690a6","tid":102463,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep